        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">What is Frase?<span class="faq-icon"><svg><use href="#i-plus"/></svg></span></button>
          <div class="faq-answer">Frase is an AI-powered SEO content research and optimization platform. It scrapes top-ranking search results for any keyword and assembles competitor headings, word counts, questions, and topic gaps into structured content briefs in 10–20 minutes. It also includes AI writing, content scoring, Google Search Console integration, and AI visibility tracking. It does not auto-publish content.</div>
