          <div class="faq-answer">No. Frase focuses entirely on website content SEO. There are no Google Business Profile tools, no local citation management, no Maps ranking features, and no local keyword tracking.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">What is the Frase lifetime deal controversy?<span class="faq-icon"><svg><use href="#i-plus"/></svg></span></button>
